FBIS3-7655 "dreas061_d_94023" FBIS-EAS-94-061 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Mar 1994 South Korea EPB Specialists To Transfer to Foreign Minstry SK2503093394 Seoul YONHAP in English 0659 GMT 25 Mar 94 SK2503093394 Seoul YONHAP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Seoul, March 25 (YONHAP) -- The Foreign Ministry, in a bid to strengthen diplomacy on economic and trade issues, intends to take on seven officials who served at the Economic Planning Board (EPB), sources said Thursday. The Ministry recently obtained one former EPB official of grade one when the board abolished the Office of External Economic Coordination. Six other grade-four and -five officials will join the ministry after taking a governmental-transfer test, they said. "The first official accepted by the ministry has already been appointed to the Institute of Foreign Affairs and National Security," one source said. "The rest will be assigned to departments concerned with trade," he said.
